message: "If you use libirrep in academic work, please cite it as below."
title: "libirrep: SO(3)/SU(2)/O(3) representation-theory primitives for equivariant neural networks and spin systems"
type: software
version: 1.3.0-alpha
date-released: "2026-04-19"
repository-code: "https://github.com/tsotchke/libirrep"
license: MIT
authors:
